Note:
math/geometry/differential.runa
Differential Geometry Operations

This module provides comprehensive differential geometry operations including
smooth manifolds, tangent spaces, differential forms, Riemannian geometry,
curvature tensors, geodesics, connections, and geometric analysis on manifolds.

Key differential geometric foundations:
- Smooth Manifolds: CвҲһ structure with smooth atlases and transition maps
- Tangent Vectors: derivations at points, tangent bundle TM = вӢғ_{pвҲҲM} T_pM
- Differential Forms: Пү вҲҲ О©^k(M) antisymmetric tensors, exterior derivative d
- Riemannian Metrics: g_p: T_pM Г— T_pM вҶ’ в„қ positive definite bilinear forms
- Christoffel Symbols: О“^k_{ij} = ВҪg^{kl}(вҲӮ_ig_{jl} + вҲӮ_jg_{il} - вҲӮ_lg_{ij})
- Riemann Curvature: R^l_{ijk} = вҲӮ_iО“^l_{jk} - вҲӮ_jО“^l_{ik} + О“^l_{im}О“^m_{jk} - О“^l_{jm}О“^m_{ik}
- Geodesics: curves Оі with вҲҮ_{Оі'}Оі' = 0, locally length minimizing
- Lie Derivatives: ВЈ_X measures change along vector field direction
:End Note

Import "dev/debug/errors/core" as Errors
Import "math/engine/linalg/core" as LinAlg
Import "math/engine/numerical/differentiation" as Differentiation
Import "math/engine/numerical/integration" as Integration
Import "math/engine/numerical/rootfinding" as RootFinding
Import "math/tensors/calculus" as TensorCalc
Import "math/tensors/algebra" as TensorAlgebra

